INDIAN DREAMER was forced in a bit at the break, stalked the early pace four then three wide, failed to keep pace past the five sixteenths, was floated out entering the lane and faded. SOPHIE JEAN , step slow, forward early on while off the rail, steadied off foes near the three and a half furlong marker, chased mid turn and weakened.
